txt.en: Free-roaming aurochs-bulls could provide meat and hides for the entire town of Eaworth. You should hunt some.
Free-roaming aurochs-bulls could provide meat and hides for the entire town of Eaworth.
Aurochs-bulls could provide much food for the folk of Eaworth...
Defeated aurochs-bulls in the Entwash Vale ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Hunt aurochs-bulls in the Entwash Vale

Aurochs-bulls can be found throughout the Entwash Vale, but especially in the herds to the south and the east of Eaworth.\n\nYou believe you can collect a decent bounty for the hunting of aurochs-bulls.
